tests/cmp/dc-label-empty.trp:1:27: parse error
  (while parsing DC label)
  1 | let val x = 42 raisedTo `<>`
    |                           ^
  unexpected '>`' (DC label end)
  expected ';'

Suggestion: Empty DC label is not allowed.
  DC labels must have both confidentiality and integrity components.
  Syntax: `< confidentiality ; integrity >`
  Examples:
    `< alice ; bob >`                               -- principal-based
    `< #null-confidentiality ; #null-integrity >`   -- public data
    `< #root-confidentiality ; #root-integrity >`   -- secret data

